HARMONY ELECTRON said unconsolidated sales
in February fell 20.50% to NT$288,058,000 from NT$362,325,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  2/2012           2/2011
Sales            288,058          362,325    
YOY%             -20.50%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            513,586          837,604    
YOY%             -38.68% 
=================================================================
 